, {"comment_id": "196279214", "nick_name": "竹仔", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1046848/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1046848-5.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2009-12-30", "content": "<span class=\"short\">绕啊，迷糊了。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "424736865", "nick_name": "上古的埙", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2301686/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2301686-61.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">现代主义是资本主义对日常生活物化的表现，同时又可以看作是物化给它带来的一切的乌托邦补偿。这些冲动在被唤起之前是不能被控制的，这是现代主义事业的微妙之处，为了在另一个时刻抑制它所唤起的那种现实主义，它就必须是现实主义的。詹姆逊的形势分析是很有一套。sigh不过这不能说明这书不是噩梦。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "399858274", "nick_name": "[已注销]", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/Romi1990/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2011-06-06", "content": "<span class=\"short\">最彰显詹明信野心的一部著作</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "210201458", "nick_name": "[已注销]", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1557375/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2010-01-30", "content": "<span class=\"short\">原著是很好的！不过翻译好烂！！</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "617228576", "nick_name": "头顶大波斯菊帽", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/hermesvane/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4735236-17.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar20 rating", "comment_time": "2012-12-17", "content": "<span class=\"short\">太虐了</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "868761778", "nick_name": "虾米", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/chench35/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1451073-1.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar20 rating", "comment_time": "2014