慰地觉得看不懂并非我的智商问题！</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1158735524", "nick_name": "端有点蓝", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/lyanfish/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53822178-13.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">太难看了，是因为翻译吗……文本分析像天书……</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "909631715", "nick_name": "A_cicada", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/A_cicada/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u54199604-8.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-08-08", "content": "<span class=\"short\">真的好难懂_(:з」∠)_ </span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "669421609", "nick_name": "Candy.K", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/4283326/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4283326-10.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2013-04-23", "content": "<span class=\"short\">断续读了一周，翻译的确诘屈聱牙，不过瑕不掩瑜，詹姆逊的智慧和学识令人佩服。读一本好书能活跃思想，带来良多启示，是辐射开的，这种快感是和小说完全不同的。在北大出版社刘小枫编的本＜东西方评论＞中，看到篇张旭东译的论拉康的文章，果然就明白晓畅多了。这本这次只是半懂半猜地读，留待数月后读完萨特、海德格尔、罗兰•巴特、弗洛伊德、拉康再重温吧。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1341598112", "nick_name": "三周华不注", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/xinthia/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u41429946-4.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2018-03-15", "content": "<span class=\"short\">妈de，看得怀疑自己智商</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1180096685", "nick_name": "悬浮的麦田", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/124383197/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u124383197-3.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2017-04-20", "content": "<span class=\"short\">很难读很难读，涉及到太多的文学作品了，听都没听过的，听同学说这种作品叫原典，不是二道贩子翻译改造的，没有添加任何概述和解释，所以会很难懂，不过我感觉翻译本身就已经是一道贩子了。。。虽然没看懂，但是看完还是有感觉的，文学是社会的象征性表现手段，再加上后面那部分关于作品的出现顺序和必然性，内容在大结构，存在主义还是结构主义上的倾向性，其实和科技想要什么里面关于扩展的文学作品出现顺序的必然性很像，相当于纵向去挖掘，精细阐述那个点了，挺好的书，文学类专业应该看着会轻松好多</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1337791302", "nick_name": "刘豆豆与刘星星", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/redyi/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1193245-47.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">海德格尔 文学哲学的平行，非本质化（萨特是文学先于存在本质）；德里达《被称作文学的奇怪建理》，文学处于一切边缘可以调动一切，又可以被一切调动，是现代的授权，超验，革命性。布鲁姆影响的焦虑，历史化的谱系，一个激发另一个，调动的是无形社会历史话语。没有纯粹的文学也没有纯粹的阅读。杰姆逊 文学是社会象征性行为。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1219627383", "nick_name": "irisbopp", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/60308661/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u60308661-52.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar20 rating", "comment_time": "2017-07-24", "content": "<span class=\"short\">看过几章之后我发现完全不得要领，到底是翻译的问题还是我中文阅读太差，看了评论我放心了，果然群众的眼睛是智慧的，这大长句给翻译的呀，以后看见这译者请绕路</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1042636375", "nick_name": "nanaxxm", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/43748947/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43748947-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2016-05-17", "content": "<span class=\"short\">不如直接看综述</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1339538525", "nick_name": "瞳.", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/cailynlv/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1274717-12.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">这个翻译真的是好烂…</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1517637422", "nick_name": "曾大勇", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/waterzeong/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u32767776-7.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar20 rating", "comment_time": "2018-11-11", "content": "<span class=\"short\">本雅明怎么为马克思代言了？康拉德就是康德</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1061842559", "nick_name": "一只小企鹅", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/122709969/", "head_image": 